revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yarbers}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yarber'' is the 10258<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 3142 individuals. ''Yarber'' is most common among White (68.87%) and Black/African American (25.11%) individuals. ===Anagrams=== * {{anagrams|en|a=aberry|brayer|ebrary}}
